---
title: Double-Stacked BBQ Beef Burgers with Spiced Sweet Potatoes and Pickles
description: Slow and smoky BBQ in one speedy bite! Flavourful beef burgers loaded with lots of BBQ sauce and classic dill pickles! All of the kiddos' favourite flavours... with a bit of spring mix for good measure.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bbq-burgers-b1f3fa86.jpg
